file.name: openapi.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.3
info:
  title: test
  version: 1.0.0
  description: test
  license:
    name: Apache 2.0
    url: https://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0.html
servers:
  - url: https
paths:
  /test:
    post:
      summary: test
      operationId: doTest
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              type: object
              properties:
                callbackURL:
                  type: string
      responses:
        '202':
          description: Accepted
        '400':
          description: An error response
      callbacks:
        notification:
          '{$request.body#/callbackURL}':
            post:
              summary: 'Creation completed'
              requestBody:
                required: true
                content:
                  application/json:
                    schema:
                      type: object
                      properties:
                        id:
                          type: string
              responses:
                '200':
                  description: OK
                '400':
                  description: An error response
